Output assets/cli-demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 900
Set Height 420
Set Padding 40
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set CursorBlink true
Set TypingSpeed 45ms

Hide
Type "skill-eval() { bash simulate_run.sh; }"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "skill-eval loop"
Sleep 200ms
Enter

Sleep 7.5s
